      <title>民意调查显示，英国选民认为，无论谁赢得选举，都可能加税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/uk-voters-see-tax-hikes-likely-whoever-wins-election-poll-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项最新民意调查显示，英国民众认为工党政府提高税收的风险与保守党政府几乎相同，这使得人们对英国大选前保守党经常使用的攻击路线产生了怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/uk-voters-see-tax-hikes-likely-whoever-wins-election-poll-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾反对党推动法案破坏新总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/taiwan-s-opposition-party-pushes-bill-to-undermine-new-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾立法者即将辩论一项法案，该法案将以牺牲新总统的利益为代价来扩大立法者的权力，并有可能引发芯片中心的大规模抗议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/taiwan-s-opposition-party-pushes-bill-to-undermine-new-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:39:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国对美国利用冻结的俄罗斯资产换取乌克兰资金的计划表示欢迎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/germany-warms-to-us-plan-to-tap-frozen-russian-assets-for-ukraine-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国官员态度大转变，准备支持美国利用冻结的俄罗斯资产产生的未来收入的计划——大部分滞留在欧洲——据知情人士透露，支持向乌克兰提供 500 亿美元的援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/germany-warms-to-us-plan-to-tap-frozen-russian-assets-for-ukraine-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在每月竞选筹款中首次领先拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/trump-leads-biden-in-monthly-campaign-fundraising-for-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普上个月筹集的资金在本次选举周期中首次超过乔·拜登，但总统的竞选团队仍然比他的共和党竞争对手拥有广泛的财务优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/trump-leads-biden-in-monthly-campaign-fundraising-for-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 02:14:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登敦促共和党领导人恢复特朗普反对的移民法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/biden-urges-mcconnell-johnson-to-revive-immigration-bill-opposed-by-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登周一在电话中敦促参众两院共和党领导人重启一项在唐纳德·特朗普宣布反对后失败的两党移民措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/biden-urges-mcconnell-johnson-to-revive-immigration-bill-opposed-by-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 01:01:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度侨民努力为八千英里外的莫迪赢得选票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/india-s-global-diaspora-is-mobilized-for-modi-s-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在华盛顿郊外一栋郊区房屋的地下室里，克里希纳·拉朱 (Krishna Raju) 和其他志愿者坐在一张折叠桌旁，从打印的名单上读出电话号码，并为 8000 多英里外的选举发出竞选号召。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/india-s-global-diaspora-is-mobilized-for-modi-s-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
